dashboardItems.text:
The objective of the "*AFI - Data quality - Discrepancies on the enrollment*" visualization is to enable the possibility to spot possibles inconsistency between the case reported on the "_Screening_" dataset (aggregate data) and the "_AFI - Acute Febrile Illness_" tracker program(individual data) at Health Facility level.

The indicator used, *DQ - Discrepancies on the enrollment*, compare the enrolled cases reported from both aggregate and individual data and in case of incongruities return a value different from 0 (Formula used: _Aggregate data_ *MINUS* _Individual data_).

A legend has been applied to facilitate the identification of possibles mistakes (highlighted in red)
